<template><div class="grid"><section class="hero galaxy-card span12"><h2>你好，我是<br><span class="gradient-text">Live Assistant</span></h2><p>你的个性化AI直播语音伙伴。支持声音训练、文本转语音、直播脚本、OBS直播支持、反馈评价与数据统计。</p><div class="quick-grid"><button class="quick" @click="$router.push('/voices')"><b>声音训练</b><span>上传音频克隆声线</span></button><button class="quick" @click="$router.push('/tts')"><b>TTS合成</b><span>用个人声音朗读文本</span></button><button class="quick" @click="$router.push('/live')"><b>直播面板</b><span>OBS与实时播报</span></button><button class="quick" @click="$router.push('/scripts')"><b>脚本排练</b><span>话术编辑与计时</span></button></div></section><section class="galaxy-card metric span3"><p>声音模型</p><strong>{{voices.length}}</strong><p>就绪/训练中</p></section><section class="galaxy-card metric span3"><p>TTS次数</p><strong>{{stats.ttsCount||0}}</strong><p>本周累计</p></section><section class="galaxy-card metric span3"><p>平均评分</p><strong>{{stats.avgRating||0}}</strong><p>用户反馈</p></section><section class="galaxy-card metric span3"><p>转化率</p><strong>{{stats.conversionRate||'--'}}</strong><p>直播数据</p></section><section class="galaxy-card span8"><h3 class="section-title">最近声音模型</h3><table class="neon-table"><thead><tr><th>名称</th><th>说明</th><th>状态</th><th>操作</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr v-for="v in voices" :key="v.id"><td>{{v.name}}</td><td>{{v.description}}</td><td><span :class="['status',v.status==='就绪'?'ready':'']">{{v.status}}</span></td><td><el-button link @click="$router.push('/tts')">使用</el-button></td></tr></tbody></table></section><section class="galaxy-card span4"><h3 class="section-title">核心流程</h3><el-timeline><el-timeline-item type="primary">注册 / 登录</el-timeline-item><el-timeline-item type="success">上传音频并训练</el-timeline-item><el-timeline-item type="warning">输入文本生成语音</el-timeline-item><el-timeline-item type="primary">直播面板实时播报</el-timeline-item></el-timeline></section></div></template>
